			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Asian Steampunk is a growing genre and has been around for a while.  Have you watched &#8216;The Good, the Bad, and the Weird&#8217;?  It came out in 2008.  If you haven&#8217;t watched it yet, I completely recommend it.  I can only describe it as a Korean Western with a dash of Steampunk.</p>
